              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Track SEO metrics (rankings, organic traffic, impressions) alongside UX and conversion metrics (bounce rate, time-on-page, conversion rate, Core Web Vitals scores) simultaneously. Combined analysis reveals whether search visitors find genuine value.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">What is the most common SXO failure?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Ranking for a keyword but mismatching search intent. If users searching "dentist near me" land on a blog post about dental history instead of a service page with contact options, they bounce immediately — signaling to Google that your page did not satisfy the query.</p></div></div>
          </div>
